I keep telling him the risks,
but he won't listen.

18:23.880 --> 18:27.000
I knew that already.
He told me himself at Samuel's party.

18:27.080 --> 18:29.080
-He told you at the party?
-See?

18:29.160 --> 18:30.640
For fuck's sake!

18:30.720 --> 18:32.520
He's telling everyone
because he wants to use you.

18:32.600 --> 18:34.760
He wants to fuck you over. Period.

18:36.400 --> 18:37.680
Nobody uses me.

18:38.720 --> 18:39.960
He won't use me.

18:50.560 --> 18:52.520
When we were little, we were good friends.

18:55.200 --> 18:56.120
Hi.

18:57.280 --> 18:58.320
Can I sit?

18:58.400 --> 18:59.400
Sure, silly.

19:01.160 --> 19:04.400
But then,
we drifted apart and we barely spoke.

19:05.120 --> 19:06.480
How are you doing?

19:08.280 --> 19:09.240
You know...

19:10.240 --> 19:12.080
I really think you were brave.

19:12.720 --> 19:15.440
And I'm sorry you had to go through
all this by yourself.

19:15.520 --> 19:19.800
Don't worry. I had Guzmán and my parents.

19:20.080 --> 19:23.600
Besides, it's been a long time
since we were close, so...

19:23.720 --> 19:26.320
But you can always count on me.
You know that, right?

19:26.920 --> 19:30.880
So, you didn't notice any changes,
anything unusual?

19:32.240 --> 19:34.160
I could really use a friend.

19:34.480 --> 19:36.000
I told you, we didn't talk.

19:37.400 --> 19:40.640
I need so many things right now...

19:41.680 --> 19:43.320
To talk, to vent...

19:43.400 --> 19:45.080
I totally understand.

19:45.360 --> 19:47.640
Would you like to meet up later?

19:47.720 --> 19:50.760
-At your house or...
-Sure. At my house. Great.

19:50.920 --> 19:51.800
OK.

19:59.000 --> 20:00.120
Yes, it's me.

20:03.200 --> 20:04.040
Hi.

20:05.400 --> 20:06.640
I couldn't find you.

20:06.920 --> 20:09.760
-How are you doing?
-What are you doing here?

20:10.080 --> 20:12.840
I couldn't stand any more pitying
or condescending looks.

20:14.240 --> 20:16.000
Did you see how Nadia stared at me?

20:16.440 --> 20:18.640
I was making a friend,
and I've already lost her.

20:19.800 --> 20:23.200
I'm sorry. You had to say it
in front of everyone because of me.

20:23.600 --> 20:25.680
It had to happen sooner or later.

20:26.760 --> 20:27.640
And...

20:30.800 --> 20:32.480
do you know when you think that...

20:32.760 --> 20:36.360
you're brave,
but the truth is you act like a coward?

20:36.640 --> 20:39.880
Saying it in front of the class like that
wasn't a cowardly thing to do.

20:39.960 --> 20:42.240
Samuel,
I'm only brave when I'm forced to be.

20:43.240 --> 20:45.320
So in the end, I have to thank you.

20:49.560 --> 20:52.800
And... are you really afraid
of being with me because I have HIV?

20:53.360 --> 20:55.280
That doesn't scare me at all, OK?

20:56.120 --> 20:57.040
OK.

20:59.120 --> 21:01.720
