to your ex.

21:02.160 --> 21:03.160
What?

21:03.840 --> 21:07.040
Or any guy you've been with,
and that you'll realize I'm just a kid.

21:07.120 --> 21:10.760
-Samuel, we are the same age.
-Sure, but we're from different worlds.

21:10.840 --> 21:11.760
What worlds?

21:11.840 --> 21:14.880
People from your world have lived
like seven lives more than I have.

21:15.640 --> 21:17.440
Samuel, you're a sweetheart.

21:18.520 --> 21:22.680
-I could do it right here.
-No. No, our first time has to be great.

21:22.760 --> 21:24.640
-And it will!
-Let me set it up.

21:25.680 --> 21:27.080
Calm down.

21:42.880 --> 21:46.520
-Hi.
-What are you doing here?

21:47.520 --> 21:49.080
I came to see you.

21:53.800 --> 21:55.440
You were a bit harsh in class,

21:55.520 --> 21:59.160
-with everything that happened.
-You didn't tell me about your sister.

22:00.920 --> 22:03.360
That's her business. I didn't tell anyone.

22:04.120 --> 22:06.880
You didn't do anything, either.
I thought you were friends.

22:07.800 --> 22:09.600
I didn't say anything
because I care about her.

22:10.080 --> 22:11.800
-If it were anyone else...
-What?

22:16.480 --> 22:19.480
-Nothing. It doesn't matter.
-What's going on, Nadia?

22:23.560 --> 22:26.120
This only makes me see
how different we are.

22:26.760 --> 22:28.840
I don't know why I'm with people like you.

22:28.920 --> 22:29.920
People like me?

22:30.480 --> 22:31.800
What does that mean?

22:35.880 --> 22:38.640
You tried to win a bet at my expense.

22:39.640 --> 22:43.560
Then, you tell me about your father
snorting coke in the cellars.

22:43.880 --> 22:45.840
And now, your sister with HIV.

22:46.000 --> 22:47.920
And you say that our culture is archaic.

22:48.000 --> 22:50.040
So your family's perfect,
everything's great?

22:50.120 --> 22:52.960
No, I'm not saying that we're perfect,
nor that it's great.

22:53.360 --> 22:55.520
But we don't have
those kinds of problems.

22:55.600 --> 22:56.840
Those kinds of problems.

22:58.320 --> 22:59.160
Hello.

23:03.520 --> 23:06.160
Yes, that will be €1.50, please.

23:06.240 --> 23:07.800
-Thanks.
-See you.

23:19.600 --> 23:23.200
Do you know what your brother is up to?
He deals drugs and sucks cock.

23:25.040 --> 23:26.080
Have a nice day.

23:30.640 --> 23:33.360
-What did he want?
-Nothing.

23:39.080 --> 23:42.400
-Carla, thanks for everything.
-No worries. It's the least I could do.

23:47.200 --> 23:48.400
Let's have a drink.

23:49.640 --> 23:50.480
Yeah, sure.

23:54.120 --> 23:55.400
Beer or wine?

23:55.800 --> 23:58.320
My mother speaks highly
of the last harvest.

23:58.400 --> 24:00.360
-Wine it is, then.
-Great.

24:04.480 --> 24:06.160
Shit, there's none left.

24:06.640 --> 24:09.400
-I'll go to the cellar for another one.
-OK.

24:09.560 --> 24:10.760
I'll be right back.

24:24.560 --> 24:27.760
If my mom finds out I've opened
one of the good ones, she'll kill me.

24:29.000 --> 24:30.200
Marina?

24:31.040 --> 24:34.440
It looks exactly the same.
It's been a long time since I last came.

24:35.440 --> 24:37.480
It's still the same mausoleum.

24:40.000 --> 24:44.920
-Well, here's to...
-To friendship in shitty times.

24:47.080 --> 24:48.040
Thank you.

24:52.440 --> 24:53.640
Omar, can we talk?

24:54.840 --> 24:55.720
Yeah.

24:58.280 --> 25:01.520
I don't know how to ask you this,
so I'll do it quick.

25:02.960 --> 25:04.000
Are you dealing drugs?

25:06.000 --> 25:07.120
Who told you that?

25:10.280 --> 25:12.560
Samuel. That fucking son of a bitch!

25:12.800 --> 25:14.560
Samuel knows? So it's true?

25:15.840 --> 25:17.360
I'm going to stop, don't worry.

25:17.440 --> 25:20.080
What were you thinking,
getting involved with that? Why?

25:27.080 --> 25:29.040
Do you know you can talk to me?

25:30.480 --> 25:31.520
About anything.

25:32.720 --> 25:36.360
I don't know, Nadia.
We've never really been the kind to talk.

25:38.080 --> 25:40.920
I know. But you can talk to me.

25:41.440 --> 25:42.400
About anything.

25:42.920 --> 25:45.800
I promise I'll listen to you...
and help you.

25:46.560 --> 25:48.760
Great. I'm going to do my homework.

25:49.040 --> 25:50.480
Take care of the store.

25:52.440 --> 25:54.320
And... there is something else, right?

26:00.760 --> 26:01.840
Do you like guys?

26:04.880 --> 26:07.840
Listen, if you do,
you'll distance yourself from Mom and Dad.

26:07.920 --> 26:10.120
With everything they've done for us!

26:10.320 --> 26:14.320
-I have the right to live my own life.
-Set it aside for a couple of years!

26:14.400 --> 26:16.040
It can't be that difficult.

26:17.040 --> 26:18.200
Look at me.

26:19.280 --> 26:21.280
I'm not an ice cube like you.

26:32.200 --> 26:33.040
Guzmán.

26:34.240 --> 26:35.080
Hey.

26:37.000 --> 26:37.880
Hey!

26:40.160 --> 26:41.000
Surprise!

26:42.000 --> 26:43.240
What are you doing here?

26:43.320 --> 26:46.800
Is the alcohol in the usual place?
I can make the best margaritas.

26:49.600 --> 26:52.040
Lu... I don't feel like it.

26:52.600 --> 26:54.360
I get it. It's normal.

26:55.120 --> 26:59.640
You've protected Marina your whole life,
and now this.

27:00.400 --> 27:02.280
You need to get your mind off it.

27:02.360 --> 27:04.200
Someone who gets you,
who doesn't judge.

27:04.280 --> 27:06.160
I'm here to listen, you know.

27:06.240 --> 27:09.120
We can watch a movie...

27:09.200 --> 27:10.320
-How about it?
-Lu.

27:10.960 --> 27:12.400
I'm not in the mood, OK?

27:12.720 --> 27:13.920
I want to be alone.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.560
Don't you miss what we had?

27:21.280 --> 27:23.680
I'm not talking about the sex, that aside.

27:24.840 --> 27:26.320
I'm talking about us.

27:27.520 --> 27:28.400
You and me.

27:29.040 --> 27:31.680
You get me better than anyone,
and I get you.

27:33.280 --> 27:34.520
We're a team.

27:40.360 --> 27:42.720
I won't allow us to lose that.

27:46.160 --> 27:47.640
-Sorry.
-Sure.

27:49.200 --> 27:51.320
Hi, Guzmán, I just wanted...

27:52.120 --> 27:53.240
to apologize.

27:53.760 --> 27:55.960
I know I've been harsh, and I'm sorry.

28:00.640 --> 28:01.720
I'm done, Lu.

28:04.560 --> 28:05.400
Lu?

28:10.280 --> 28:12.920
Here we go again. What?

28:13.520 --> 28:15.320
-What?
-Get out of the pool room.

28:15.400 --> 28:17.400
-I can't hear you.
-Fine, I'm coming.

28:20.240 --> 28:21.480
Lu, not now.

28:23.280 --> 28:25.880
I just think you're really boring.

28:26.600 --> 28:28.360
Can you stop fooling around, please?

28:29.520 --> 28:31.440
Besides, we're not alone.

28:31.840 --> 28:34.480
I'm turning one of your worst days...

28:34.920 --> 28:35.920
into a good one.

28:37.160 --> 28:38.520
-Bye.
-No!

28:41.400 --> 28:42.360
No way!

28:44.080 --> 28:46.600
-Come in with me!
-No, Lu. I don't want to.

28:46.800 --> 28:49.040
Just for a little while. Don't be boring!

28:49.120 --> 28:50.840
I want you to leave.

28:53.600 --> 28:56.840
OK, then. Help me get out.
I can't swim with shoes on.

28:57.520 --> 28:59.720
-Don't do what you're thinking about.
-I won't.

29:02.920 --> 29:04.120
I knew it.

29:04.720 --> 29:08.960
Of course you knew. You know why?
Because you can't help it.

29:09.920 --> 29:13.680
Because we can hook up with other people,
we can be with other people,

29:14.160 --> 29:17.600
but you and me...
will always be you and me, honey.

29:18.880 --> 29:21.160
Right? Come on, give me a kiss.

29:21.560 --> 29:23.720
-No.
-Kiss me.

29:49.880 --> 29:51.800
Tomorrow, the house will be empty, OK?

29:51.880 --> 29:53.920
Her parents are away.
Carla will be in class.

29:54.000 --> 29:56.760
The code for the alarm is 1-6-4-9.

29:56.840 --> 29:58.600
I'll text it to you later.

29:58.680 --> 30:03.040
To get the watches, go up the stairs
to her parents' bedroom.

30:03.240 --> 30:05.640
There is a bathroom
with a dressing room inside.

30:05.720 --> 30:08.360
In the dressing room,
there'll be some drawers,

30:08.440 --> 30:09.880
and the watches will be there.

30:14.840 --> 30:16.680
1-6-4-9.

30:16.920 --> 30:18.040
That's it.

30:18.800 --> 30:20.400
-Bye.
-Bye.

30:22.920 --> 30:24.360
-They told me to come.
-Really?

30:24.440 --> 30:27.520
-I'm telling you.
-What a nice chat you're having.

30:27.600 --> 30:29.720
He has a casting call tomorrow.

30:30.520 --> 30:31.880
Did you set it up?

30:33.000 --> 30:35.000
Yeah, with my mother.

30:35.560 --> 30:38.200
Of course you did. Thanks so much, man!

30:38.280 --> 30:40.520
By the way, I don't know what to wear.

30:40.600 --> 30:43.600
Well, the less you wear
and the more you show, the better.

30:44.000 --> 30:47.040
Don't you think, Polo?
You like him better undressed, right?

30:48.040 --> 30:50.600
-What are you talking about?
-Let's go to class.

30:51.800 --> 30:52.920
Thanks a lot.

30:54.160 --> 30:55.040
You're welcome.

30:57.560 --> 30:59.920
LET ME KNOW WHEN YOU GET THEM.

31:00.160 --> 31:04.120
-No! Did you get it?
-You know me.

31:04.200 --> 31:05.240
What's going on?

31:05.920 --> 31:07.720
Nothing, Lu was telling me...

31:08.640 --> 31:11.280
-She gets everything she wants.
-Don't say anything.

31:11.360 --> 31:13.600
-What?
-I'm talking about Martín.

31:13.760 --> 31:15.960
She has him eating out of the palm
of her hand.

31:16.040 --> 31:16.880
Martín? Why?

31:17.440 --> 31:18.560
-Tell her.
-No.

31:18.640 --> 31:19.760
I'll tell you myself.

31:19.840 --> 31:24.480
She got him connections in the embassy
to expedite the adoption process.

31:25.080 --> 31:26.200
Seriously?

31:26.480 --> 31:29.160
Yes, I'm his favorite again. As always.

31:30.320 --> 31:33.120
Poor thing,
he was going about it the honest way,

31:33.200 --> 31:36.600
but when you don't have money,
honesty's a luxury you can't afford.

31:37.960 --> 31:38.920
Yeah.

31:39.000 --> 31:41.960
Oh, Marina!
I'm really happy we're friends again.

32:17.120 --> 32:18.160
Fucking great!

32:26.720 --> 32:30.440
Don't you tell me...
That's a fucking bummer.

32:34.240 --> 32:35.200
Damn girl...

32:35.800 --> 32:38.840
Nothing to do all day.
They don't even let you use the Internet.

32:47.160 --> 32:48.440
They needed to spice it up.

32:56.680 --> 32:59.240
Not at all.
I'm not sure why I wanted to go there.

32:59.320 --> 33:01.440
I'm taking a shower,
and I'll be right there.

33:01.520 --> 33:03.360
OK? See you in a bit.

33:40.000 --> 33:42.000
I'VE GOT THEM.

33:59.360 --> 34:00.720
Shit!

34:06.040 --> 34:08.280
-Are you going to tell us?
-Tell you what?

34:08.360 --> 34:11.840
-Carla and Lu tell each other everything.
-It was nothing. Just a mistake.

34:12.200 --> 34:14.520
A mistake, period. Please, drop it.

34:14.600 --> 34:16.120
-A mistake?
-A mistake.

34:16.200 --> 34:17.640
-OK.
-Please.

34:18.360 --> 34:19.280
OK.

34:19.920 --> 34:20.800
It's your friend.

34:22.080 --> 34:22.960
Hey.

34:24.480 --> 34:28.200
How are you doing?
