-What do you think?

34:59.600 --> 35:02.760
-Don't go. I'm giving you my blessing.
-Who asked for your blessing?

35:02.840 --> 35:05.120
-Don't leave, please.
-Omar!

35:05.440 --> 35:07.560
Blessing?
It's not like you're their best man.

35:10.000 --> 35:11.560
Omar, they're my friends.

35:11.640 --> 35:13.680
-Hi. What's wrong?
-Omar!

35:15.760 --> 35:18.040
-How are you doing?
-Hi.

35:22.720 --> 35:24.720
-What?
-I'm a bit nervous.

35:25.280 --> 35:27.640
-Don't be. Why?
-I don't know.

35:28.280 --> 35:30.240
-Wait for me. I'm out in five minutes.
-OK.

35:30.320 --> 35:31.240
See you in a bit.

35:35.960 --> 35:37.920
Omar, let's just talk about it.

35:41.000 --> 35:44.480
Why did you tell people we're together?
No, no.

35:44.560 --> 35:47.200
Besides, where did you even get that idea?

35:47.280 --> 35:49.840
-They're my friends.
-We're not together!

35:50.280 --> 35:52.600
It's not happening, Ander.
Not now, not ever.

35:54.720 --> 35:59.720
-I don't get why you're acting like this.
-Because I can't do this.

36:00.160 --> 36:03.160
Too many people know.
Even my sister, man.

36:03.560 --> 36:07.720
And you don't know my family.
If they knew, I'd break their hearts.

36:09.240 --> 36:13.400
-I thought nobody dies of a broken heart.
-Hi.

36:14.600 --> 36:15.520
Omar, right?

36:15.600 --> 36:18.920
-Yeah.
-Can you sell me something?

36:19.000 --> 36:20.840
I think we might need it.

36:23.600 --> 36:26.160
-How much?
-It's on the house.

36:26.640 --> 36:27.960
But be careful with it.

36:28.040 --> 36:30.920
It's strong,
and we don't want you to get sick.

36:32.120 --> 36:32.960
Thanks.

36:36.800 --> 36:37.680
Everything OK?

36:40.120 --> 36:41.000
Yes.

36:51.640 --> 36:52.560
Wait.

36:56.440 --> 36:58.160
What do you think?
Are the lights too much?

36:59.200 --> 37:00.280
No, it's nice.

37:10.720 --> 37:13.160
I've got pot. You want some?

37:13.240 --> 37:14.920
-No, we're fine.
-OK.

37:28.840 --> 37:30.320
-Samuel...
-What?

37:31.000 --> 37:32.080
More slowly.

37:32.480 --> 37:33.320
OK.

37:39.760 --> 37:40.640
Fuck!

37:41.040 --> 37:42.320
What? Just relax.

37:42.840 --> 37:44.400
I can't believe this.

37:45.800 --> 37:46.960
I'm fucking it up.

37:48.000 --> 37:49.680
-I'm fucking up.
-Lay down.

38:02.600 --> 38:03.720
Samuel.

38:04.280 --> 38:05.200
Yes?

38:06.440 --> 38:07.640
I want to love you.

38:33.960 --> 38:36.520
-Sorry.
-Relax.

38:36.920 --> 38:38.440
-Sorry.
-It's all right.

38:40.200 --> 38:42.160
I wasn't so bad, right?

38:43.040 --> 38:44.880
No. You were great.

38:45.680 --> 38:46.560
Really great.

38:48.160 --> 38:49.840
Samuel, I should leave soon.

38:52.200 --> 38:56.600
-My mom works tonight.
-Yes, but they're expecting me for dinner.

39:10.480 --> 39:17.240
Don't freak out, but someone broke in.
They took the watches and...

39:19.480 --> 39:21.120
they took mine, too.

39:23.880 --> 39:25.920
Yes, everything is in there.

39:27.640 --> 39:30.520
-What's all this?
-I have enough to pay it all off.

39:30.600 --> 39:31.720
Where did you get them?

39:31.800 --> 39:34.120
-Let's say Marina helped me open a door.
-What?

39:34.200 --> 39:36.560
Why did you drag her into this?

39:37.080 --> 39:39.160
Fuck! Why did she get involved?

39:39.240 --> 39:41.680
Because she loves you. Why else?

39:42.240 --> 39:45.800
I'm telling you, it's going to be okay.
So be happy for me,

39:45.880 --> 39:49.480
because I'm fixing everything with this.
It's about time.

39:49.800 --> 39:52.520
Pun intended. This one's for you.

39:52.600 --> 39:54.400
-Put it away.
-It smells like rich people.

39:54.480 --> 39:55.320
OK.

39:56.440 --> 39:57.440
Man.

40:16.000 --> 40:18.240
<i>I just wanted to make sure</i>
<i>you got home safe.</i>

40:19.280 --> 40:20.400
I had a great time.

40:22.080 --> 40:23.800
We can talk before going to bed.

40:24.400 --> 40:25.240
<i>Bye.</i>

41:15.760 --> 41:16.680
Hi, Guzmán.

41:17.120 --> 41:17.960
Hi.

41:18.040 --> 41:20.640
How is your sister?
She didn't come to the first class.

41:21.200 --> 41:24.200
-I guess she overslept. I'm not sure.
-Look who it is.

41:25.800 --> 41:30.440
You were great in your pool last night.
Sometimes I forget how good we are in bed.

41:30.520 --> 41:32.480
So you did it to tell everyone, right?

41:32.720 --> 41:36.480
-You don't surprise me anymore, Lu.
-Was it a secret?

41:36.760 --> 41:40.200
Well, I thought there were no secrets
between friends.

41:41.000 --> 41:42.080
See you later.

41:44.560 --> 41:45.400
Nadia...

41:45.480 --> 41:48.280
-Don't worry.
-It was nothing.

41:49.720 --> 41:51.600
-Just you?
-Yes.

41:51.880 --> 41:52.720
Hey.

41:53.200 --> 41:55.880
I called three times.
My name wasn't on the casting list.

41:58.840 --> 42:02.080
In the end, it didn't work out.
My mom wasn't sure about you. Sorry.

42:02.600 --> 42:04.160
Yeah, fucking great.

42:05.520 --> 42:07.080
Did you really ruin that for him?

42:07.720 --> 42:11.240
Yeah.
What's wrong? I don't owe him anything.

42:11.320 --> 42:15.320
Besides, I'm tired of him using us.
He wants to take advantage of us.

42:15.400 --> 42:17.120
Like we're not using him?

42:17.200 --> 42:18.880
What's really bothering you?

42:19.680 --> 42:21.360
He only wants us for one thing.

42:21.640 --> 42:23.680
-Right.
-In fact, he only wants you.

42:24.200 --> 42:25.280
You're jealous.

42:25.680 --> 42:26.960
What are you saying?

42:29.680 --> 42:30.520
Marina.

42:32.920 --> 42:34.000
How are you doing?

42:34.200 --> 42:37.440
I kept calling you last night.
I called you this morning, too.

42:37.520 --> 42:38.400
Is everything OK?

42:38.480 --> 42:41.080
Yeah, I was just tired, and my phone died.

42:42.840 --> 42:43.720
Sure.

42:45.400 --> 42:48.760
Sure what, Samuel?
You don't believe me?

42:48.840 --> 42:52.040
It's not that. I'm starting
to get the feeling you're avoiding me.

42:52.120 --> 42:56.600
-Don't get paranoid, Samuel.
-Paranoid about what?

42:56.680 --> 42:58.480
I'm starting to feel like an idiot.

42:58.960 --> 43:00.600
If something is going on, don't lie.

43:00.680 --> 43:02.760
The only thing I can't stand
is being lied to.

43:06.760 --> 43:10.360
That's the only thing you can't stand?
Lies?

43:11.480 --> 43:13.400
Fuck, you can't stand much!

43:13.720 --> 43:16.800
Because lies make life easier.

43:17.640 --> 43:20.640
To avoid pain, to avoid suffering.
To avoid hurting people.

43:22.440 --> 43:24.640
-Drop it.
-I'm not sure... Marina!

43:25.800 --> 43:26.920
Marina!

43:31.760 --> 43:32.720
Marina!

44:11.000 --> 44:13.560
That's my boy.
I didn't expect any less from you.

45:11.600 --> 45:12.480
Marina!

45:12.640 --> 45:14.000
Marina, are you OK?

45:14.560 --> 45:16.920
-Fuck!
-Why did you argue?

45:17.600 --> 45:20.120
I'd never been close to anyone
with HIV.

45:20.880 --> 45:23.240
Marina!

45:23.600 --> 45:26.360
Marina. What happened?
What are you doing? Go get help!

45:26.440 --> 45:28.520
Marina, look at me.

45:28.600 --> 45:29.520
Martín!

45:29.600 --> 45:31.600
Look at me!

45:31.680 --> 45:34.280
Move over, I've got this. Come on.

45:35.080 --> 45:36.640
Can you hear me? Look at me.

45:37.120 --> 45:39.960
Look at me. Follow my finger, please.

45:40.040 --> 45:41.240
Marina!

45:41.720 --> 45:44.280
Fuck, look at those pupils. Damn it.

45:44.760 --> 45:47.240
What did you take, Marina?
What did you take?

45:48.000 --> 45:49.440
What happened with Marina?

45:52.560 --> 45:56.800
You know this means immediate expulsion?
We have a zero-tolerance drug policy.

45:56.880 --> 45:58.840
-No, don't.
-I'm taking you to the nurse.

45:58.920 --> 46:00.600
-I don't want to.
-We're going.

46:00.680 --> 46:02.520
I'm fine. I'm perfectly fine.

46:04.240 --> 46:06.240
Are you sure
you didn't have a relationship

46:06.320 --> 46:07.720
with Marina outside of class?

46:08.040 --> 46:09.760
No, of course not.

46:09.840 --> 46:12.200
I'm taking her to the hospital.
Tell administration.

46:12.280 --> 46:15.160
-Let's go.
-Martín, no! No!

46:21.080 --> 46:22.640
If you tell anyone,

46:22.720 --> 46:25.640
I'll tell them about your deal with Lu.
The adoption.

46:31.160 --> 46:32.200
Wait.

46:41.280 --> 46:43.680
Of course,
it's not fair what they did to her.

46:44.080 --> 46:45.440
No one deserves that.

46:49.360 --> 46:50.920
Did you hate Marina?

